{"tid":822052,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"湯洛雯水着瘦番晒！","createTime":"2018-09-16T06:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T07:01:21.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6891044a719f9e11318228a26749510233c1b2","tid":822052,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"藝人湯洛雯（靚湯）前晚在社交網分享水着照，穿上黑色低胸一件頭泳衣、外面配以白色魚網衫的她浸在水中，身材若隱若現，十分誘人！靚湯還感性留言：「常常說女人是水造的。女人和水，好像有某種天然聯繫；清純如水，溫柔如水，柔韌如水，靈動如水，善變如水。」不少網民留言大讚她非常漂亮，又指雖然早前有指她分手後身形脹爆，惟見其水着照身形依然纖瘦，索爆！"},{"pid":"6c96ae291640c362afc90344fd421cc9d40cd957","tid":822052,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:58:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"710aead83a497d407c9eae558e7e0501361df50f","tid":822052,"uid":35926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:58:13.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7c41e0e94af295e3caf6bbe6ae4c820a605d4cde","tid":822052,"uid":195393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"650bc8722d8c1710c84d744a786ae33f2dfc962d","tid":822052,"uid":59375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"無圖學乜人開post?"},{"pid":"97ea4056f420c6eead408a49c9b58f8e281e0215","tid":822052,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"0f37d6bdecc02e8bbe06097f23a967546d31c158","tid":822052,"uid":206590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f3267ae2bd2b5d2e90b8d5dbb374645d95dd601","tid":822052,"uid":147522,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/150119_6d246800d971d264088489160d5bfbab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F150119_6d246800d971d264088489160d5bfbab.png&h=d50296